/**
 * T-50 ÔÇö Unit tests for ProvisionManagementUserUseCase.
 *
 * Written FIRST (TDD red phase) ÔÇö fails before the use-case exists.
 *
 * Verifies:
 * - Actor role read from STUBBED ScopeContextHolder.current() (NOT DTO body).
 * - SYSTEM_ADMIN ÔåÆ GERENCIA: OK (no rank restriction on super-role).
 * - TALENTO_HUMANO ÔåÆ GERENCIA: throws ForbiddenException (privilege-escalation).
 * - TALENTO_HUMANO ÔåÆ TALENTO_HUMANO: OK.
