/**
 * T-80 ÔÇö Org management integration suite (WU-8 FINAL GATE).
 *
 * Covers Deliverables D1ÔÇôD4 from the org-structure spec.
 *
 * D1 ÔÇö Role-scoped Zone/Municipio READ endpoints
 *   Scenario 1.1: GLOBAL_ROLES see all zones (>= 2 seeded zones)
 *   Scenario 1.2: COORDINADOR sees only their zone
 *   Scenario 1.3: COORDINADOR sees only their zone's municipios (Zona Urab├í ÔåÆ 8)
 *   Scenario 1.4: GLOBAL_ROLES see all 13 seeded municipios
 *   Scenario 1.5: SUPERVISOR ÔåÆ 403 (no org-level read permission)
 *   Scenario 1.8: COORDINADOR with missing zoneId ÔåÆ empty list (fail-closed)
 *   Scenario 1.9: COORDINADOR cannot see other zone's municipios
 *
 * D2 ÔÇö Assign/Reassign COORDINADOR to a Zone
 *   Scenario 2.1: Fresh assignment success (SYSTEM_ADMIN)
 *   Scenario 2.2: Reassignment ÔÇö previous holder cleared, @unique not violated
 *   Scenario 2.4: GERENCIA caller ÔåÆ 403
 *   Scenario 2.5: Non-COORDINADOR target user ÔåÆ 400
 *   Scenario 2.6: Non-existent zone ÔåÆ 404
 *   Scenario 2.8: TALENTO_HUMANO caller successfully assigns
 *   Scenario 2.9: SUPERVISOR caller ÔåÆ 403
 *   Scenario 2.10: COORDINADOR caller ÔåÆ 403
 *
 * D3 ÔÇö Management-User Provisioning (incl. privilege-escalation)
 *   Scenario 3.1: SYSTEM_ADMIN ÔåÆ GERENCIA (201, mustChangePassword=true)
 *   Scenario 3.2: SYSTEM_ADMIN ÔåÆ LIDER_OPERATIVO (201)
 *   Scenario 3.3: blocked role SUPERVISOR ÔåÆ 400
 *   Scenario 3.5: duplicate email ÔåÆ 409
 *   Scenario 3.6: route-level GERENCIA caller ÔåÆ 403
 *   Scenario 3.9: TALENTO_HUMANO ÔåÆ TALENTO_HUMANO (201)
 *   Scenario 3.10: TALENTO_HUMANO ÔåÆ LIDER_OPERATIVO (201)
 *   Scenario 3.11: TALENTO_HUMANO ÔåÆ GERENCIA ÔåÆ 403 (MANDATORY: proves request-scoped DI + escalation guard)
 *   Scenario 3.12: SYSTEM_ADMIN provisions all three management roles
 *
 * D4 ÔÇö ScopedMunicipioRepository coverage via /org/municipios endpoint
 *   Scenario 4.1: COORDINADOR municipio read uses ScopedMunicipioRepository (own zone only)
 *   Scenario 4.2: GLOBAL_ROLES receive all municipios (pass-through)
 *   Scenario 4.3: Unknown role is denied (fail-closed)
 *
 * JWT minting: uses the same mintToken() pattern from scope-isolation.int-spec.ts
 * (dev JWT_SECRET fallback; tokens bypass the login endpoint to avoid argon2 roundtrips
 * per fixture user). Device sessions are created for all principals.
 */

